Message: Welcome to werewolv.es! This is an extended game mode where a day's play takes a full 24 hours to complete (12 hour day/night). The game will last around a week (on average). When the game is due to start an email will be sent out to alert all players. New players will be kicked at this time and will need to rejoin the game through the link in the email.

This game may have a complicated or unknown setup and we recommend not taking part in this if it's your first game, try a game starting with 'wlf' instead. If you want to play a quicker game where days last only a few minutes, check the #speed-games channel on our Discord server
This game's daytime will be from 09:00 until 21:00 UTC
